Package: PRSfromPGS
Title: Calculate Polygenic Risk Scores from PGS Catalog Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("PRSfromPGS Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "placeholder@example.com")
Description: Calculates Polygenic Risk Scores (PRS) from genetic data. Reads
    genotype dosage data from bgzipped VCF files and applies PGS Catalog-format
    scoring models to produce per-sample risk scores.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
